&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="若离开了对觉悟二字的信仰正真之道必成群盲的迷途"&gt;&lt;span&gt;若离开了对“觉悟”二字的信仰，正真之道必成群盲的迷途&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e8%8b%a5%e7%a6%bb%e5%bc%80%e4%ba%86%e5%af%b9%e8%a7%89%e6%82%9f%e4%ba%8c%e5%ad%97%e7%9a%84%e4%bf%a1%e4%bb%b0%e6%ad%a3%e7%9c%9f%e4%b9%8b%e9%81%93%e5%bf%85%e6%88%90%e7%be%a4%e7%9b%b2%e7%9a%84%e8%bf%b7%e9%80%94" class="heading-mark"&gt;
